📊 Student Performance Tracker (Streamlit)

A Student Performance Tracker built using Python and Streamlit that allows users to analyze and visualize student academic performance. The application provides interactive dashboards, performance insights, and easy data tracking for students or educators.

This project demonstrates how data analysis and visualization can help monitor academic progress effectively using modern Python tools.

🚀 Features

📈 Track student academic performance

📊 Visualize marks using charts and graphs

📂 Manage student data

📉 Analyze trends in student results

🖥️ Interactive web interface using Streamlit

🛠️ Tech Stack

Python

Streamlit
📊 Example Use Cases

Teachers tracking class performance

Students analyzing their academic progress

Educational data visualization projects

